AutoHonor is a World of Warcraft bot. 

The bot is created to Farm honorpoints by auto joining battlegrounds.

The bot comes with the following Features:

* Auto join Random Bg
* Release Spirit
* Leaves Battleground
* Set your own Macros(the bot will frequently use them)
* No AFK
* Auto Walk
* Set Delay between actions
* Set your own Mouse Clicks
 
Safety:

AutoHonor is Very safe to use as it only controlls your mouse & keyboard. Therefore it doesn't touch Game Files at all. 

It will look like you used your mouse & keyboard.
